'''''Jock of the Bushveld,''''' ni filimi yasohotse muri 1986  [[Afurika y’Epfo|yo muri Afurika y'Epfo]] <ref>https://www2.bfi.org.uk/films-tv-people/4ce2b80e58c73</ref>, iyoborwa na  Gray Hofmeyr itunganywa amashusho na  Duncan MacNeillie hamwe na  Duncan MacNeillie Production na Toron International<ref>http://www.gautengfilm.org.za/news/news-archive/2010/november-2010/699-jock-of-the-bushvelds-happy-ending-in-animated-3d</ref>. Muri iyi filime hagaragaramo Jonathan Rands, Jocelyn Broderick na Michael Brunner mu mwanya wa mbere hamwe na Gordon Mulholland, Wilson Dunster mu nshingano zunganira n'imbwa "Umfubu".<ref>https://diary.wine.co.za/diary.aspx?DIARYID=18293&CLIENTID=4823</ref> Iyi filime ishingiye ku gitabo cyanditswe n'umwanditsi wo muri Irilande James Percy FitzPatrick wagiye muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika]] y'Epfo mu myaka ya 1800 kandi akibonera ibintu byinshi byabereye mu mashyamba<ref>https://www.filmcontact.com/south-africa/johnny-clegg-writes-music-jock-bushveld</ref>. 

== Umugambi ==
Mu 1886, Percy Fitzpatrick w'imyaka 20 ukomoka mu mujyi wa Cape Town yerekeje ku kirwa cya Delagoa muri Transvaal gucukura zahabu<ref>https://moviefit.me/titles/26838-jock-of-the-bushveld</ref>. Agezeyo, abuza icyana cy'imbwa, Jock, kurohama arakirera<ref>https://www.cinematerial.com/movies/jock-of-the-bushveld-i2306589/p/set6daek</ref>. Iyo amaherezo Percy ageze iyo yerekeza, nta zahabu iba ikiriho, nuko atangira kuba umuyobozi. Nyuma yaho, we na Jock babayeho mubyabaye byinshi birimo inyamaswa zo mwishyamba hamwe nabashoferi batwaraga abacakara<ref>https://www.reverbnation.com/keithhutchinson/song/26301781-film-music-jock-bushveld-1986</ref>.  

